# Implementation Plan - Dynamic Appointment Slots & Booking Window Limits

Implement a calendar booking window range (dates selection) configurable by the clinic admin/doctor, dynamic first-come-first-served time slot generation, and real-time double-booking slot exclusion.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> A new Entity Framework migration is required to add `BookingWindowEndDate` (DateTime?, nullable) to the `Clinics` table. 
> Existing records will default to null (no limit on booking range, or up to 30 days max booking).

## Open Questions
- None.

